      "rationale": "Reynolds-averaged Navier-Stokes with SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on literature consensus for rotary blood pump flows. Non-Newtonian blood rheology modeled using Carreau model with parameters from literature. Power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) applied. Model form assumptions documented and consistent with MRL 2 requirements."
